%p
  Paste the CAP XML document in the text box below:
%form{ :action => '/validate', :method => 'post' } 
  %textarea{ :id => 'cap_data', :name => 'cap_data', :rows => 25 }= h( @cap_data )
  %p
    %input.validate_button{ :type => "submit", :value => "Validate" }
    %a.clear_button{ href: "#" }Clear

%p
  Provide a URL pointing to a CAP XML document on the web:
  %form{ :action => '/validate_url', :method => 'post' } 
    %input{ :name => 'cap_data_url', :size => 50, :value => @cap_data_url }
    %input.validate_button{ :type => "submit", :value => "Validate" }

%p
  Try these sample CAP XML documents:
%ul
  %li
    %a{ :href => validate_file_path( 'east_bay_wind_cap.xml' )} Wind Advisory for Northern California Coast, USA
  %li
    %a{ :href => validate_file_path( 'ottawa_roads_cap.xml' )} Road Conditions Advisory for Ottawa, Canada
  %li
